snippet.description:

In this landmark episode, Gobinath sits down with the one and only Ulaganayagan Kamal Haasan—a legend who redefined Indian cinema with fearless creativity, profound intellect, and unmatched versatility.

From shaping every genre with groundbreaking performances to living and breathing cinema with unwavering passion, Kamal Haasan is not just an actor—he is a movement. A voice like no other, his bold choices, deep-rooted philosophy, and lifelong dedication to the arts have inspired generations across borders.

In this deep, honest, and insightful conversation, Kamal Haasan reflects on:
• His journey of constant reinvention
• Staying true to his beliefs against all odds
• Tamil pride and global recognition
• The influence of icons like Sivaji, Kannadasan, Periyar, and Kalaignar
• His thoughts on AI and the future of creativity
• What it truly means to give everything for one’s craft
• His eternal quest to learn, evolve, and create

He also opens up about his unshakable love for cinema, and what continues to drive him decades into his journey.

A must-watch for every cinema lover, thinker, artist, and dreamer.
